Reviewed-by: Jun Li <jun.li@nxp.com>
Acked-by: Felipe Balbi <balbi@kernel.org>
Signed-off-by: Jack Pham <jackp@codeaurora.org>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20210812082635.12924-1-jackp@codeaurora.org
